description:
You Were Born Rich has been going strong for nearly 30 years. I am so happy you can access the entire seminar here.

I love this program because it reminds us of something powerful that we have long forgotten.

Even though we were all born rich, soon after our birth, we were programmed to forget our rich heritage. And then we often start to struggle through life as if it were hard. What a shame!

The good news is, with this phenomenal program, you’ll be able to reclaim your birthright and begin to thrive.

You Were Born Rich has helped millions of people earn millions of dollars, and live happier, more fulfilled lives. So don’t dismiss these videos. Set aside time to watch and study each one so you can reap the riches inside of you
